769
00:57:43,400 --> 00:57:45,300
Every place he worked.

770
00:57:46,700 --> 00:57:49,700
Newfoundland. Baffin Bay.

771
00:57:50,400 --> 00:57:53,400
Glasgow. Liverpool. Narvik.

772
