774
00:58:03,300 --> 00:58:05,600
<i>with Moran Brothers Tug and Salvage.</i>

775
00:58:05,700 --> 00:58:09,600
<i>The old ship had been refitted with</i>
<i>a diesel engine and a new sea winch.</i>

776
00:58:09,700 --> 00:58:12,600
<i>We went around Florida</i>
<i>and up the Atlantic seaboard.</i>

777
00:58:12,700 --> 00:58:16,100
<i>We were a crew of seven now.</i>
