there's nothing left to enjoy.

918
01:09:00,300 --> 01:09:04,700
And now, take a little swallow of vodka
while it's still in your mouth.

919
01:09:19,500 --> 01:09:22,400
You haven't been with many women,
have you?

920
01:09:23,600 --> 01:09:25,200
Not on Sundays.

921
01:09:27,400 --> 01:09:29,100
