No, ma'am.

923
01:09:36,700 --> 01:09:38,400
When I was 19,

924
01:09:39,400 --> 01:09:45,700
I attempted to become the first woman
ever to swim the English Channel.

925
01:09:46,700 --> 01:09:48,100
Really?

926
01:09:48,700 --> 01:09:51,700
But the current that day
was so strong that,

927
01:09:51,800 --> 01:09:54,900
for every stroke I took,
I was pushed back two.

928
01:09:55,500 --> 01:09:58,100
<i>I was in the water for 32 hours.</i>

929
01:09:59,100 --> 01:10:02,900
And when I was two miles from Calais,

930
01:10:04,100 --> 01:10:05,800
<i>it started to rain.</i>

931
01:10:06,600 --> 01:10:08,500
That's it! Steady on!

932
01:10:09,000 --> 01:10:11,600
<i>When I couldn't go any further,</i>

933
01:10:13,200 --> 01:10:14,700
I stopped.

934
01:10:16,100 --> 01:10:17,700
<i>I just stopped.</i>

935
01:10:18,300 --> 01:10:23,100
And everybody asked me,
would I try again?

936
01:10:23,900 --> 01:10:25,700
<i>For why wouldn't I?</i>

937
01:10:28,600 --> 01:10:30,300
But I never did.

938
01:10:31,800 --> 01:10:36,000
As a matter of fact, I've never done
anything with my life after that.

939
01:10:40,200 --> 01:10:42,200
Your hands are so coarse.

940
01:10:52,500 --> 01:10:55,100
I can feel the wind in your cheek.

941
01:11:01,900 --> 01:11:04,400
I'm afraid it's the witching hour.

942
01:11:10,300 --> 01:11:13,500
<i>It was the first time</i>
<i>a woman had ever kissed me.</i>

943
01:11:14,100 --> 01:11:16,500
<i>It's something you never forget.</i>

944
01:11:27,000 --> 01:11:29,000
I think you make me feel younger.

945
01:11:29,100 --> 01:11:31,700
You make me feel years younger, too.

946
01:11:31,800 --> 01:11:33,400
I wish I was.

947
01:11:34,400 --> 01:11:36,500
So many things I'd change.

948
01:11:37,200 --> 01:11:39,500
I'd undo all my mistakes.

949
01:11:39,600 --> 01:11:41,300
What mistakes?

950
01:11:44,700 --> 01:11:46,800
I kept waiting, you know?

951
01:11:47,500 --> 01:11:52,000
Thinking that I'd do something
to change my circumstances.

952
01:11:53,300 --> 01:11:55,000
Do something.

953
01:11:56,600 --> 01:11:59,800
Such an awful waste.
You never get it back.

954
01:12:00,300 --> 01:12:01,700
Wasted time.

955
01:12:08,000 --> 01:12:10,400
If we're going to have an affair,

956
01:12:11,200 --> 01:12:14,000
