during the day.

957
01:12:14,600 --> 01:12:17,600
And we're always to part before sunrise.

958
01:12:18,300 --> 01:12:20,900
And we will never say "I love you."

959
01:12:22,500 --> 01:12:24,300
Those are the rules.

960
01:12:26,900 --> 01:12:29,100
- Are you cold?
