961
01:12:29,200 --> 01:12:31,100
Oh, you! You're frozen.

962
01:12:31,200 --> 01:12:34,400
What an idiot, I'm standing here
in this fur. How thoughtless of me.

963
01:13:08,100 --> 01:13:10,900
<i>She was the first woman</i>
<i>that ever loved me.</i>

964
01:13:13,900 --> 01:13:15,100
You want me to skip some?

965
01:13:15,200 --> 01:13:21,000
No, I'm glad he had somebody
to keep him warm.

966
01:13:24,700 --> 01:13:27,100
"I couldn't wait to see her again."

967
01:13:40,000 --> 01:13:42,300
<i>We saw each other every night.</i>

968
01:13:42,900 --> 01:13:45,200
<i>We always used the same room.</i>

969
01:13:47,200 --> 01:13:50,500
<i>But each time seemed new</i>
<i>and different.</i>

970
01:13:51,900 --> 01:13:53,400
Come here.

971
01:14:00,900 --> 01:14:02,300
Elizabeth.

972
01:14:03,600 --> 01:14:05,000
Good night.

973
01:14:07,700 --> 01:14:09,400
<i>Until one night.</i>

974
01:14:46,600 --> 01:14:52,200
<i>Yesterday, December 7th, 1941,</i>

975
01:14:52,300 --> 01:14:55,400
<i>a date which will live in infamy...</i>

976
01:14:55,500 --> 01:14:59,700
