that there was only
a short window of time you could do it.

1535
02:10:14,400 --> 02:10:16,900
So, even if nothing ever happened,

1536
02:10:17,000 --> 02:10:20,100
you'd still be right here
where you are now.

1537
02:10:20,200 --> 02:10:22,400
I just don't like getting old.

1538
02:10:24,000 --> 02:10:26,500
They put too much chlorine in here.

1539
02:11:07,800 --> 02:11:11,700
I promise you I'll never lose myself
to self-pity again.

1540
02:11:16,000 --> 02:11:19,100
And I think right there and then

