1571
02:14:40,000 --> 02:14:43,200
I'm just not sure how to reconcile this.

1572
02:14:43,300 --> 02:14:45,400
Would you tell a blind man
he couldn't have children?

1573
02:14:45,500 --> 02:14:47,100
Here you go.

1574
02:14:47,200 --> 02:14:50,600
You'll be a father for as long as you can.

1575
02:14:50,700 --> 02:14:53,500
I know the consequences.
