1652
02:23:32,700 --> 02:23:36,200
We can make the best or the worst of it.

1653
02:23:36,300 --> 02:23:38,600
And I hope you make the best of it.

1654
02:23:41,700 --> 02:23:44,400
I hope you see things that startle you.

1655
02:23:46,600 --> 02:23:50,100
I hope you feel things
you never felt before.

1656
02:23:52,600 --> 02:23:56,000
I hope you meet people
with a different point of view.

1657
02:23:57,200 --> 02:23:59,900
I hope you live a life you're proud of.

1658
02:24:02,900 --> 02:24:08,000
And if you find that you're not,
I hope you have the strength

1659
02:24:08,100 --> 02:24:11,300
- to start all over again.
