1660
02:24:12,800 --> 02:24:16,500
He had been gone a long time.

1661
02:24:18,300 --> 02:24:20,400
I'll see you next Thursday.

1662
02:24:23,400 --> 02:24:26,800
- Good night, Miss Daisy.
